IF
See([PC])
Global("AC#PPMesmerAnkheg","GLOBAL",0)
THEN
RESPONSE #100
SetGlobal("AC#PPMesmerAnkheg","GLOBAL",1)
DisplayStringHead(Player1,~(When you approach the ruins, you notice an ankheg that looked as if it was lured by the place, but when the creature notices you, it decides to attack.)~)  
END
